        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">

            <p>Your interview is scheduled for <strong>Model.SignedUpSlotInformation.Date.ToString("dddd d MMMM yyyy")</strong> at <strong>Model.SignedUpSlotInformation.Description</strong>.</p>
            <br />
